((3) 0 () 0 () () (u . "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n  <meta name=\"format-detection\" content=\"telephone=no\">\n\n  <script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"/functions.js\"></script>\n\n  <meta content=\"Contact | Alexander Nabavi-Noori\" name=\"title\" />\n  <meta content=\"Contact Alexander Nabavi-Noori.\" name=\"description\" />\n  <meta content=\"website\" property=\"og:type\" />\n  <meta content=\"https://alexandernnoori.com/contact.html\" property=\"og:url\" />\n  <meta content=\"Contact | Alexander Nabavi-Noori\" property=\"og:title\" />\n  <meta content=\"Contact Alexander Nabavi-Noori.\" property=\"og:description\" />\n  <meta content=\"summary_large_image\" property=\"twitter:card\" />\n  <meta content=\"@xandernn\" property=\"twitter:site\" />\n  <meta content=\"https://alexandernnoori.com/contact.html\" property=\"twitter:url\" />\n  <meta content=\"Contact | Alexander Nabavi-Noori\" property=\"twitter:title\" />\n  <meta content=\"Contact Alexander Nabavi-Noori.\" property=\"twitter:description\" />\n\n  <link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico\" />\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" media=\"all\" href=\"/fonts/fonts.css\" />\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" media=\"all\" href=\"/styles.css\" />\n\n  <title>Contact | Alexander Nabavi-Noori</title>\n\n  <style type=\"text/css\">\n    #switcher {\n      margin-top: 12px;\n      border: 1px solid gray;\n      box-shadow: 2px 2px;\n      cursor: default;\n      text-align: center;\n      padding-top: 0.2em;\n      padding-bottom: 0.2em;\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n\n<body id=\"body\" class=\"body-text_century-supra\">\n\n  <div id=\"switcher\"><a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"index.html\">About</a>\n<a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"research.html\">Research</a>\n<a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"experience.html\">Experience</a>\n<a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"blog.html\">Blog</a>\n<a class=\"nav-link active\" href=\"contact.html\">Contact</a>\n<a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"/ANabaviNoori_CV.pdf\">CV</a>\n</div>\n\n  <div id=\"content\">\n\n    <div id=\"doc\"><div id=\"doc\"><p><title-block><topic class=\"small\">Con\u00ADtact</topic><short-rule>I am gen\u00ADer\u00ADally reach\u00ADable by email for ques\u00ADtions about my research, teach\u00ADing, office hours, or pro\u00ADfes\u00ADsional mate\u00ADri\u00ADals.</short-rule></title-block></p><div class=\"subhead\" id=\"reachme\"><a href=\"#reachme\">reach Me</a></div><p>The best way to reach me is via email at <span class=\"no-hyphens\"><span class=\"font-triplicate-code\"><a href=\"mailto:xandernabavinoori@fas.harvard.edu\">xan\u00ADdern\u00ADabavi\u00ADnoori@fas.har\u00ADvard.edu</a></span></span></p><p>You can also sign up for a meet\u00ADing with me via my <a href=\"https://calendly.com/alexander-nnoori/30min\">Cal\u00ADendly.</a></p><p>My office is located at:<br/><span class=\"font-triplicate-code\">1737 Cam\u00ADbridge Street</span><br/><span class=\"font-triplicate-code\">CGIS Knafel, Office K___</span><br/><span class=\"font-triplicate-code\">Cam\u00ADbridge, MA. 02138</span></p><div class=\"subhead\" id=\"scholarship\"><a href=\"#scholarship\">aca\u00ADd\u00ADe\u00ADmic pro\u00ADfiles</a></div><p>Here is the lat\u00ADest ver\u00ADsion of my <a href=\"https://alexandernnoori.com/ANabaviNoori_CV.pdf\">Cur\u00ADricu\u00ADlum Vitae.</a></p><p>You can also usu\u00ADally find drafts of my work\u00ADing law review arti\u00ADcles on my <a href=\"https://papers.ssrn.com/Sol3/Cf_Dev/AbsByAuth.cfm?per_id=3365919\">Social Sci\u00ADence Research Net\u00ADwork (SSRN)</a> page.</p><p>The rest of my work lives on <a href=\"https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=ia12OScAAAAJ&amp;hl=en\">Google Scholar.</a></p><p>Code for var\u00ADi\u00ADous of my side projects can be found on my <a href=\"https://github.com/alexandernnoori\">GitHub</a> page, includ\u00ADing a <a href=\"https://github.com/alexandernnoori/remarkable-zotero\">project</a> that syncs Zotero cloud accounts with Remark\u00ADable e-ink tablets.</p><div class=\"subhead\" id=\"elsewhere\"><a href=\"#elsewhere\">else\u00ADwhere</a></div><p>For those want\u00ADing even more, catch me on <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/alexandernoori/\">LinkedIn</a> or <a href=\"https://bsky.app/profile/xandernn.bsky.social\">Bluesky.</a></p></div></div><a id=\"links\"></a>\n    <div class=\"gap\" style=\"height:1em\"></div>\n    <ul class=\"children\"></ul>\n\n  </div>\n\n  <div id=\"toolbar\" class=\"\">\n\n    <div id=\"navtable\">\n\n      <div>\n        <a class=\"box-link\" href=\"colophon.html\"><span class=\"arrow\">←</span>&nbsp;colophon</a>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"center\">\n        <a class=\"box-link\" href=\"/\">home</a>\n      </div>\n\n      <div>\n        <a class=\"box-link\" href=\"/ANabaviNoori_CV.pdf\">curriculum vitae&nbsp;<span class=\"arrow\">→</span></a>\n      </div>\n\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n</body>\n\n</html>"))